  { q: 'Which mini-split brands do you install?', a: 'We install Mitsubishi Electric, Fujitsu, LG, Daikin, and Gree. For most Wesley Chapel and Tampa homeowners we recommend Mitsubishi or Fujitsu for the best field reliability and parts pipeline in Florida. Daikin is a strong value option. We stay away from Amazon-only budget brands; servicing them a few years in is genuinely hard.' },
