  { q: 'Do I need a permit to install a mini-split in Pasco or Hillsborough County?', a: 'Yes. Both counties require a mechanical permit for new split-system installations, including ductless mini-splits. We pull the permit, coordinate the inspection, and include permit cost in the written quote. Skipping it often gets flagged later on a home-sale 4-point inspection.' },
