  { q: 'What kind of warranty comes with the install?', a: 'Mitsubishi, Fujitsu, LG, and Daikin all offer 10 or 12-year parts warranties when registered by a factory-authorized installer at the time of install, which we do on install day. Our labor warranty is 2 years on the installation itself. Warranties require annual maintenance records; we include a first-year tune-up.' },
];

