  <h2>Brands we install, ranked by Tampa field reliability</h2>
  <p>These rankings come from the several hundred mini-splits on our maintenance rolls across <a href="/service-areas/pasco-county-ac-repair/">Pasco</a>, <a href="/service-areas/hillsborough-county-hvac-company/">Hillsborough</a>, and Polk counties:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Mitsubishi Electric:</strong> best overall reliability in Florida humidity, strongest parts pipeline, cleanest installs. Our default for most homes.</li>
    <li><strong>Fujitsu Halcyon:</strong> very close to Mitsubishi on reliability, often better pricing, excellent multi-zone flexibility.</li>
    <li><strong>LG:</strong> strong mid-tier, especially the ArtCool designer heads where looks matter.</li>
    <li><strong>Daikin:</strong> solid value, most reliable in the 18k and 24k sizes.</li>
    <li><strong>Gree:</strong> the budget end we will install, only when a homeowner understands the slower warranty support.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Whichever brand fits, the <a href="/services/ac-repair-tampa/">repair</a> and <a href="/services/ac-maintenance-tampa/">maintenance</a> support behind it matters more than the badge, and we service what we install.</p>

  <ReviewQuote
